definition: to pass/to spend (time)/to survive/to get through
to pass/to spend (time)/measure/limit/extent/degree of intensity/degree (angles, temperature etc)/kilowatt-hour/classifier for events and occurrences
to cross/to go over/to pass (time)/to celebrate (a holiday)/to live/to get along/excessively/too-

sentences.english: He spent his golden years traveling to many parts of the world.
sentences.chinese: 他通過周遊世界度過了晚年的幸福時光。

sentences.english: The Dunnings have a wealth of stories from the time they spent with Jackson.
sentences.chinese: 鄧寧斯有一段與傑克遜共同度過的寶貴的人生經歷。

sentences.english: I remember when I went and I had a great time.
sentences.chinese: 我記得我讀大學的時候度過了一段美妙的時光。

sentences.english: We are trying to help out by delivering flour to bakeries.
sentences.chinese: 我們正在設法給麪包店送去麪粉，幫助它們度過難關。

sentences.english: He told a heart-wrenching story of his childhood in the impoverished countryside.
sentences.chinese: 他講述了在貧困農村度過的悲慘童年的經歷。

sentences.english: May the joy of the Sping Festival be with you throughout the year.
sentences.chinese: 願新春佳節的喜悅，伴隨您度過新的一年。

sentences.english: Let's pretend that you spend the evening out on the town.
sentences.chinese: 假設你在要在城裏度過一晚。

sentences.english: Would I have to spend the rest of my life blind in one eye?
sentences.chinese: 我是否要在失去一隻眼睛視力的情況下度過餘生？

sentences.english: Last summer I spent a month in Switzer.
sentences.chinese: 去年夏天我在瑞士度過了一個月。

sentences.english: She spent her girlhood in the country.
sentences.chinese: 她少女時期是在鄉下度過。

sentences.english: And so that's how we spent our first Christmas here,
sentences.chinese: 我們就是這樣在這兒度過我們的第一個聖誕節的。

sentences.english: Gravida can pass through pregnant period with treatment.
sentences.chinese: 經採取相應治療措施後孕婦能度過妊娠期。

sentences.english: The nudists will enjoy their beautiful summer day at the resort of Usedom.
sentences.chinese: 遊客將在烏塞敦的裸體村莊內度過夏日愜意的一天。

sentences.english: Some days are for living, other are for getting through.
sentences.chinese: 有些日子是月用耒享受的，另一些日子只是度過而己。

sentences.english: This year's New Year's eve, I was spent in shaoxing grandma's.
sentences.chinese: 今年的除夕，我是在紹興奶奶家度過的。

sentences.english: My landlord’s daughter and I would create a unique nativity of our own.
sentences.chinese: 房東的女兒和我共同度過了一個特別的聖誕節。
